c: 46
v: 20
t: "And on the Day that the Unbelievers will be placed before the Fire, (It will be said to them): \"Ye received your good things in the life of the world, and ye took your pleasure out of them: but today shall ye be recompensed with a Penalty of humiliation: for that ye were arrogant on earth without just cause, and that ye (ever) transgressed"